26/07/2009
TIRANA, Albania -- Police arrested on Friday (July 24th) 58 members of a drug smuggling group, including 28 Albanians.
About 80kg of heroin, cocaine and marijuana were seized in the operation, and two illegal drug laboratories were busted.
The drugs, which were smuggled into Italy from Albania, were hidden in truck tires.
One of the Albanians arrested was wanted based on an international arrest warrant.
His identity was not revealed.
(MIA, Makfax - 24/07/09)
